<div class="help_template">
<div class="title"> NEW WHO IS WHO LINKS</div>
<p>Use this page to set up a new Who is Who link. </p>
  <p> <img src="{!URLFOR($Resource.ulw_help_pop_up, 'img/help_image_8.jpg')}"/> </p>

 <table width="800" border="0" cellpadding="4">
  <tr>
    <td class="bubblebox"><span class="numcolor">1</span></td>
    <td class="bubbletxt"><span>Give the link a name that will be displayed on the page
.</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bubblebox"><span class="numcolor">2</span></td>
    <td class="bubbletxt"><span>Provide the URL to where your team details sit. This could be to a SharePoint site. 
 </span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bubblebox"><span class="numcolor">3</span></td>
    <td class="bubbletxt"><span>Give a description for the link.</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bubblebox"><span class="numcolor">4</span></td>
    <td class="bubbletxt"><span>Select "Save” to save the Brand Link or “Cancel” to cancel the changes you have made.</span></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bubblebox"><span class="numcolor">5</span></td>
    <td class="bubbletxt"><span>The Ordinal is where this link will sit in the Who is Who section. Input a number between  0 and 99. 0 being at the top of the list and  99 being bottom.</span></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</div>
